==English==
===Etymology===
Old English ''[[spere]]''

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ЙӘЙҷ(r)|-ЙӘЙҷ(r)]]

===Noun===
'''spear''' (pl. ''spears'')

# A long stick with a sharp tip used as a weapon for throwing or thrusting.
# A long tool used by fishermen to retrieve fish

